{"tid":564140,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手要狠 比相戀勇敢","createTime":"2018-02-17T15:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T16:43:29.000Z","uid":84117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d07c9d8255a7a3e6b5eeea88cee04819277ede","tid":564140,"uid":84117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"同前度分手三個禮拜了，被分手嘅我，由每日喊到食唔到、訓唔到，到而家每日依然會諗起佢，試過去佢公司樓下等佢，打電話比佢，send msg比佢，明明係佢做錯事，我仲係好想同返佢一齊⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我知道要放低佢喇，但我每日都係忍唔住text佢，想同佢復合⋯⋯<br />\n其實講分手嘅你，可唔可以唔好再覆我嘅wts，唔好再對我咁好，唔好再話做返朋友。<br />\n<br />\n被分手果個一定會好掛住對方，一定好想復合，仲要佢地忍住唔好搵返前度，到底點做到？<br />\n<br />\n分手要狠，好不好啊？"},{"pid":"227b36a2b1d0f4150eb4cf3822ecce86c4163132","tid":564140,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"未扮成弱者去挽留 就永遠給你自由<br />\n時候註定要放手 就應該放手"},{"pid":"86fec202912518b48e11a3a11e79f87285242f79","tid":564140,"uid":84117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"227b36a2b1d0f4150eb4cf3822ecce86c4163132","tid":564140,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"未扮成弱者去挽留 就永遠給你自由<br />\n時候註定要放手 就應該放手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"分手的禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日係咁聽 <br />\n係咪時間會令自己放手？我自問呢一刻做唔到"},{"pid":"4c992865a832d55eaf808b853fbccd9dab3c53a9","tid":564140,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86fec202912518b48e11a3a11e79f87285242f79","tid":564140,"uid":84117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"227b36a2b1d0f4150eb4cf3822ecce86c4163132","tid":564140,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"未扮成弱者去挽留 就永遠給你自由<br />\n時候註定要放手 就應該放手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"分手的禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl